Whippin’ the Chiron ft. the matching Veyron 😈😈😈 #Bugatti 
Video by @thestradman 

#cars #car #carlifestyle #carsofinstagram #carswithoutlimits #supercar #supercars #hypercar #hypercars

Feel all the power, energy and speed of the Bugatti Chiron on your luxury watch! @jacobandco 🔥

The @JacobandCo . Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon is a timepiece designed to honor the Chiron hyper sportscar. The tonneau-shaped case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the animated "engine block," is intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine. This engine, which operates on demand, as well as the rest of the caliber, is completely visible under a massive sapphire crystal. There are several finishes for the sleek case, including the warm glow of traditional rose gold and the modern blue metallic finish of titanium.

Available at @jacobandco 🚀

What a Beauty 😍 @jacobandco 

BUGATTI Chiron Tourbillon Rose Gold has a 55mm-by-45mm case made of highly polished 18K rose gold. 😍 Its tonneau shape is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron hyper sports car, giving it a sleek, aerodynamic appearance.  Inside is a replica of the BUGATTI 16-cylinder engine visible through sapphire crystal. 💎

 In 2019, Bugatti and @JacobandCo . formed a long-term partnership to create unique timepieces. The Bugatti Chiron is one of those watches. In just two years, the two companies have produced nearly 10 models of this timepiece inspired by the Chiron hyper sportscar. The engine animation, flying tourbillon on a 30-degree incline and the sleek case design are among the features that seamlessly merges high-speed automobiles and haute horlogerie.

Introducing the breathtaking @jacobandco Twin Turbo Furious Bugatti... 😍

A true grand complication, the Twin Turbo Furious Bugatti combines two tourbillons, a monopusher chronograph with a decimal minute repeater. What makes this last complication different is that most minute repeater chime out the hours, quarter-hours and minutes, while a decimal repeater sounds the hours, the TENS of minutes and then the minutes.

Available at @jacobandco 🔥
